                    <h3 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4 mt-5">CHAPTER 4: CONSEQUENCES OF UNSAFE WORK</h3>

                    <p class="lead">Your High Risk Work Licence is a privilege that comes with serious responsibilities. The work health and safety regulator has the power to take action if you fail to work safely.</p>

                    <div class="chapter-section mt-4">
                        <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3">What Can Happen If You Work Unsafely</h4>

                        <p>If you breach safety requirements while performing high risk work, the regulator can:</p>

                        <div class="consequences-section mt-4">
                            <div class="consequence-card">
                                <div class="consequence-header suspend">
                                    <div class="consequence-number">1</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Suspend Your Licence</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="consequence-body">
                                    <p>The regulator can temporarily suspend your licence for a specified period (such as 3 months, 6 months, or longer). During suspension:</p>
                                    <ul class="consequence-list">
                                        <li>You cannot legally perform high risk work</li>
                                        <li>You cannot operate forklifts for commercial purposes</li>
                                        <li>You must not work even if an employer asks you to</li>
                                        <li>The suspension will be recorded on your licence history</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="consequence-card">
                                <div class="consequence-header cancel">
                                    <div class="consequence-number">2</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Cancel Your Licence</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="consequence-body">
                                    <p>For serious breaches or repeated violations, your licence can be permanently cancelled. If this happens:</p>
                                    <ul class="consequence-list">
                                        <li>You cannot perform high risk work</li>
                                        <li>You must complete full training and assessment again to get a new licence</li>
                                        <li>The cancellation becomes part of your permanent record</li>
                                        <li>Future licence applications may be scrutinized more carefully</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="consequence-card">
                                <div class="consequence-header refuse">
                                    <div class="consequence-number">3</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Refuse to Renew Your Licence</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="consequence-body">
                                    <p>When your licence comes up for renewal, the regulator can refuse to renew it based on:</p>
                                    <ul class="consequence-list">
                                        <li>Poor safety record during the licence period</li>
                                        <li>Outstanding safety violations</li>
                                        <li>Serious incidents you were involved in</li>
                                        <li>Pattern of unsafe behavior</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="consequence-card">
                                <div class="consequence-header reassess">
                                    <div class="consequence-number">4</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Direct You to Undertake Reassessment</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="consequence-body">
                                    <p>The regulator can require you to prove your competency again by:</p>
                                    <ul class="consequence-list">
                                        <li>Undergoing reassessment with an approved assessor</li>
                                        <li>Completing additional training</li>
                                        <li>Demonstrating you can work safely</li>
                                        <li>Paying for the reassessment yourself</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="consequence-card">
                                <div class="consequence-header prosecute">
                                    <div class="consequence-number">5</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Prosecute You</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="consequence-body">
                                    <p>For serious safety breaches, you can face legal prosecution resulting in:</p>
                                    <ul class="consequence-list">
                                        <li>Criminal charges</li>
                                        <li>Heavy fines (potentially tens of thousands of dollars)</li>
                                        <li>Imprisonment for serious offenses</li>
                                        <li>A criminal record</li>
                                        <li>Difficulty finding future employment</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

