                                    <div class="comparison-result">
                                        ‚úì Choose Route A - visibility is crucial.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="route-decision-card">
                                <h6 class="route-decision-title">üö¶ Traffic</h6>
