                        <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3">Dynamic Route Assessment</h4>
                        <p class="mb-3">Continue assessing your route during travel:</p>
                        <ul class="mb-3">
                            <li>Watch for new hazards</li>
                            <li>Monitor changing conditions</li>
                            <li>Observe other traffic</li>
                            <li>Check for obstacles ahead</li>
                            <li>Maintain awareness of your surroundings</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="mb-0"><strong>Be prepared to stop and reassess if conditions change significantly.</strong></p>
