                    <h3 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4 mt-5">CHAPTER 8: TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT</h3>

                    <div class="chapter-section mt-4">
                        <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3">What is a Traffic Management Plan?</h4>

                        <div class="alert alert-info">
                            <p class="mb-2">A <strong>Traffic Management Plan (TMP)</strong> is a documented strategy that describes how vehicles, mobile plant (including forklifts), and pedestrians move safely around a workplace.</p>
                            <p class="mb-0">The plan aims to prevent collisions and injuries by separating different types of traffic and implementing controls.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tmp-importance-box mt-4">
                            <div class="tmp-importance-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
                            <div class="tmp-importance-content">
                                <p class="mb-0"><strong>Before you begin forklift operations, you must confirm that the traffic management plan is properly implemented.</strong> This means checking that planned controls are actually in place and working.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="chapter-section mt-5">
                        <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3">Components You Must Confirm</h4>

                        <div class="tmp-components-section mt-4">
                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">1</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Designated Traffic Routes</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Specific pathways marked for vehicle traffic</li>
                                        <li>Clear lanes with visible markings</li>
                                        <li>One-way systems where appropriate</li>
                                        <li>Visible route markings and signage</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">2</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Pedestrian Walkways and Exclusion Zones</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Marked pedestrian areas separated from vehicle traffic</li>
                                        <li>Physical barriers where needed</li>
                                        <li>Clear signage identifying pedestrian zones</li>
                                        <li>Exclusion zones clearly marked and enforced</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">3</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Speed Limits</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Posted speed limits appropriate for each area</li>
                                        <li>Lower speeds near pedestrians</li>
                                        <li>Reduced speeds at intersections</li>
                                        <li>Variable speed limits for different zones</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">4</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Signage Placement</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Stop and give way signs at critical locations</li>
                                        <li>Warning signs for hazards</li>
                                        <li>Directional signs for traffic flow</li>
                                        <li>Restriction signs clearly visible</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">5</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Barriers and Bollards</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Physical protections for building structures</li>
                                        <li>Separation barriers between vehicles and pedestrians</li>
                                        <li>Guard rails at dangerous edges</li>
                                        <li>Protection for critical infrastructure</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">6</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Warning Devices</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Flashing lights on forklifts</li>
                                        <li>Reversing alarms functioning properly</li>
                                        <li>Intersection warning lights</li>
                                        <li>Communication systems in place</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">7</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Traffic Controllers and Spotters</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Trained personnel positioned where needed</li>
                                        <li>Coverage for complex maneuvers</li>
                                        <li>Spotters at busy intersections</li>
                                        <li>Controllers for loading operations</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-component-card">
                                <div class="tmp-component-header">
                                    <div class="tmp-component-number">8</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Separation of Vehicles and Pedestrians</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tmp-component-body">
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Separate entry points for vehicles and pedestrians</li>
                                        <li>Time-based separation where physical separation isn't possible</li>
                                        <li>Physical barriers preventing pedestrian access to vehicle areas</li>
                                        <li>Pedestrian-free zones during active forklift operations</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="chapter-section mt-5">
                        <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3">How to Confirm Implementation</h4>

                        <div class="tmp-confirmation-container mt-4">
                            <div class="tmp-confirmation-step">
                                <div class="tmp-confirmation-number">1</div>
                                <div class="tmp-confirmation-content">
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Obtain the TMP Document</h6>
                                    <p class="mb-0">Request the Traffic Management Plan document from your supervisor or site office. Review it to understand what should be in place.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-confirmation-step">
                                <div class="tmp-confirmation-number">2</div>
                                <div class="tmp-confirmation-content">
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Conduct Visual Inspection</h6>
                                    <p class="mb-0">Walk through your planned work area and verify each component is physically present and properly positioned.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="tmp-confirmation-step">
                                <div class="tmp-confirmation-number">3</div>
                                <div class="tmp-confirmation-content">
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Check for Changes</h6>
                                    <p class="mb-0">Look for any changes to the work area since the TMP was created. Construction, storage, or layout changes can affect the plan.</p>
